	<h1 class="title">设计这家餐厅之前，设计师先为它虚拟了一个人格</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1329/small/1329.jpg?1418779602" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">胡莹 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-26 12:37:19 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/21275/medium/21275.jpg?1453722471" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="21275" data-title="《设计这家餐厅之前，设计师先为它虚拟了一个人格》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/21275/medium/21275.jpg?1453722471" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/21275.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
		<!-- 新浪微博 -->
